reviewText: I love it and and my family do too  and the kids in my Daycare like it too  I know she did a t.v. show but had never seen it I just wish there was more

This was a birthday gift for a 4 y/o girl. The theme was the little mermaid, which was one of the stories on the DVD. No animation, real people.  Several people remembered the series and how great it was. Great gift.
This was a gift and it was well well received!!
